Name: The name the asset will have in Unity Cloud
Unity ID: The Unity ID of the asset. Only relevant to unity projects
Files: The files that will be uploaded, with the format "<file path on the computer>:<filepath in the cloud>"
Dependencies: The dependencies of the asset. For embedded dependencies, use the file column instead.
Collection: The collection the asset will be linked to
Tags: The tags that will be applied to the asset
Preview: The preview of the asset, with the format "<file path on the computer>:<filepath in the cloud>"
